{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CASTAWAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564860/extras/STEAM_CASTAWAY_page_01.gif?t=1729368385\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an <strong>action-packed adventure</strong> in Castaway, diving players into a <strong>pixelated and retro universe</strong>. Assume the role of Martin, whose spaceship crash-landed on an uncharted island where his faithful pet was taken by hostile creatures. <strong>Retrieve your weapons</strong> and venture out to <strong>rescue your kidnapped companion</strong> in this endearing and unexpectedly dynamic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>2 mini-games in 1! STORY MODE / SURVIVOR MODE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564860/extras/STEAM_CASTAWAY_page_02.gif?t=1729368385\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beat the <strong>3 bosses</strong> in the concise and delightful &quot;<strong>Story Mode</strong>&quot; to unlock the thrilling and addictive &quot;<strong>Survivor Mode</strong>.&quot; Ascend a <strong>50-floor tower</strong>, with each level presenting increasingly challenging trials!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2564860/extras/STEAM_CASTAWAY_page_03.gif?t=1729368385\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>For All Ages: </strong>From the &quot;pacifist&quot; mode without enemies or \u201cinvincible\u201d to the challenging &quot;unfair&quot; mode, Castaway caters to all ages, from seasoned gamers to younger players discovering the genre for the first time. Try to complete the game as quickly as possible thanks to the <strong>speedrun mode</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Charming Pixel Art Graphics:</strong> Immerse yourself in a 2D retro pixel art world reminiscent of classic adventure games. It'll feel like coming home!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unique Weapon Abilities: </strong>Solve puzzles by acquiring weapons with distinct characteristics - the sword for speed, the pickaxe for power, and the grappling hook for increased mobility.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enchanting Soundtrack: </strong>Enjoy chiptune melodies, whether heroic or haunting, paying homage to the 8-bit console era!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Who did it?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2564860/98c133a262463435f44890d73d60b13462c4ef24.jpg"},{"name":"Headache","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2564860/6addbc8a0e16abbf369afe68a6094d222d8e9d1d.jpg"},{"name":"Nice dive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2564860/0d85992f27ee54a176f086651da37dc5d0458a9d.jpg"},{"name":"Potato masher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2564860/278a359666b16993aa64c30969eda8736ad758a0.jpg"},{"name":"Nice backhand!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2564860/c624867e6aaf619e98ff2e0ee7d46a8439ee9765.jpg"},{"name":"Maze master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2564860/e7ea0bc537e2b8ec9c45d6eceddd1635b35f2eec.jpg"},{"name":"You found your sword!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2564860/1f595a9d474552a1c45f63a32699ddfdaeb4e4e8.jpg"},{"name":"You found your pickaxe!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2564860/c532aeeef4e05b9682e9d4f2fd309a93c8db3333.jpg"},{"name":"You found your grappling hook!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com